  m_text: "Welcome to Life Guardian!!You Have been Chosen.   \n\nIn this journey,
    you will explore the world of diabetes through choices. \nYour decisions will
    directly impact your Dew Points: make healthy choices to gain them, but beware,
    unhealthy decisions will cause you to lose them. Dew Points nourish and maintain
    the ancient Baobab Tree, the very heart of our world. Now, brave Guardian, choose
    your path forward: will you focus on Prevention or Management?"
